{"tid":1890054,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"英國自由民主黨發起聯署呼籲開放BNO申請及擁有居留權","createTime":"2020-02-21T03:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T08:19:57.000Z","uid":304769,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"75085ede93e415352faa20442e0b414775c0299f","tid":1890054,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTb739r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTb739r.png&h=38c8a828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/libdems/status/1230502868878123008?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flibdems%2Fstatus%2F1230502868878123008%3Fs%3D21&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=5ec48fc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flibdems%2Fstatus%2F1230502868878123008%3Fs%3D21&h=cc185f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/libdems/status/1230502868878123008?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nThe UK has a moral and legal duty to the people of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nThe Chinese government have reneged on the promises made to protect and enhance their rights and freedoms. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">It is time the Conservative government reopens the British National Overseas (BNO) Passport scheme and extend it to give the people of Hong Kong the right to live in the UK. </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">冇成本 點解唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.libdems.org.uk/hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.libdems.org.uk%2Fhong-kong&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=3f8de093\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.libdems.org.uk/hong-kong</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，都係重要持分者，必須engage。叫人放棄英國戰線d兒登仔同叫人區議會投白票d熱狗無分別。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要拉攏英國民意啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<br />\n爭取BNO平權救手足可以順手將英國拉向我地呢邊，何樂而不為。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8a27762b83220ab7becb3790ecd9bafd073d0847","tid":1890054,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a241f7334b315df0942a9ac0cac8efee14cdada2","tid":1890054,"uid":76270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:27:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d75a8f4c86ac9e2acd8931fd16f44a72a0174c6","tid":1890054,"uid":20684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8a15576cbbbb364b66f854ae5a61e1b7293b91c1","tid":1890054,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"Pushp"},{"pid":"2063809885d9750f9e106ce8a1081d88bc70ab25","tid":1890054,"uid":71286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bbebd4f1628154b3aa3262b6e934804542ade47","tid":1890054,"uid":321803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"推出"},{"pid":"bd5ac980fe503420ef5839001d2c1e3923473971","tid":1890054,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"簽唔到，佢卡左係sign the petition 果頁"},{"pid":"45e5cb6d214c6115328a2be9be2f87d0227b5115","tid":1890054,"uid":91957,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"要求英國宣布中國違反中英聯合聲明並收回香港"},{"pid":"80446836094e4cf8326b73be7e93e7923e699af2","tid":1890054,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:33:00.000Z","msg":"連登好多5毛、香港獨立黨嘅撚人帶風向<br />\n<br />\n利申:已簽"},{"pid":"7b0312b6a34fbe6a2db777a772647dd491e9557a","tid":1890054,"uid":196701,"like":2,"disl